    "description": "《真实攀岩》是一款由经验丰富的游戏开发者和攀岩者带来的一场终极攀岩盛会，其拟真感、沉浸感和技巧感独树一帜，在全球实地扫描的真实场景更会让您获得身临其境般的登高与攀岩体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179440/extras/9245efce910afe7a0b46a9bbdbf571f8.poster.avif?t=1772128735\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179440/extras/9245efce910afe7a0b46a9bbdbf571f8.webm?t=1772128735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179440/extras/9245efce910afe7a0b46a9bbdbf571f8.mp4?t=1772128735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>真实攀岩，惊险刺激动心魄！</strong><br>《真实攀岩》有着基于物理运算的真实攀爬机制，就像现实生活中的攀岩一样，玩家需要小心控制身体平衡才能向上攀登。感受肢体悬空时那在血管中暴走的肾上腺素，以及登顶时畅快淋漓的成就感。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179440/extras/6408fe34fc41f0bd474583f58f2a7b98.poster.avif?t=1772128735\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179440/extras/6408fe34fc41f0bd474583f58f2a7b98.webm?t=1772128735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179440/extras/6408fe34fc41f0bd474583f58f2a7b98.mp4?t=1772128735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>真实攀岩，勤勉不倦登新高！</strong><br>《真实攀岩》将带您前往现实生活中或许不会前往的崇山峻岭。在那里不断磨练自己的攀岩技术，成为专业选手，在高峰与排行榜的阶梯向上攀爬。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179440/extras/d556cb14756f174415934ece3a037d5c.poster.avif?t=1772128735\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179440/extras/d556cb14756f174415934ece3a037d5c.webm?t=1772128735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179440/extras/d556cb14756f174415934ece3a037d5c.mp4?t=1772128735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>真实攀岩，悬崖绝壁也去得！</strong><br>《真实攀岩》突破了攀岩运动的极限。您将拥有无限次的重来机会，无论是天堑般的攀爬路线还是最险恶的攀爬环境，都不再能阻止挑战者们的意志。<br><br><strong>游戏特色:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>基于物理运算的真实攀爬机制，挑战您的平衡力与落点判断力<br></li><li>在电子游戏中前往现实生活中的知名攀岩地点一爬究竟<br></li><li>无人机与摄影测量法强强联手，真实扫描名山大川<br></li><li>危险的单人攀岩体验，却安全无虞<br></li><li>现实里攀不得的地方在游戏里攀得<br></li><li>在排行榜与其他玩家一较高下<br></li><li>磨练攀岩技巧<br></li><li>征服恐高症</li></ul><br>《真实攀岩》是献给攀岩爱好者们、以及想要体验攀岩乐趣的玩家们的终极沉浸式攀岩游戏。伸手蹬脚，攀登新高！",
